<t:pageTemplate pageTitle="Help">
   <h4> Help page</h4>
    <p> ${user.username}, if you have uncertainties about how to use the app, you have come to the right place!</p>
    <h5> How do I use the calendar?</h5>
    <p> You have to click the 'Calendars' option in the main menu, you'll be taken to the page where
    you can see your calendars and the calendars you have been invited to collaborate on by one of your friends.</p>
    <p> You can either create a new calendar or check the calendars you already have.</p>

    <h5> How do I write in my diary?</h5>
    <p> You have to click on the 'Diary' option in the main menu, then you'll be prompted to your diary.
    Feel free to write anything that goes through your mind.</p>

    <h5> How do I add a friend?</h5>
    <p> You have to go to the 'Friends' tab in the main menu, then you will be able to see your friends and search
    for new ones using the search bar.</p>

    <p>... more to come</p>
</t:pageTemplate>
